;; Root.synth — exec surface (v0.18)
;;
;; Executable programs. Minimal: imports, optional consts,
;; then the main program body. Everything else referenced
;; from the aski surface.
;;
;; Delimiter allocation:
;;   ()      Module header (imports only)
;;   {||}    Const
;;   []      Program (the main process)

#Module#( @ModuleName <Module> )
*#Const#{| @ConstName <:aski:Type> @Literal |}
#Program#[ +<:aski:Statement> ]
